    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of unrivaled distinction, maintained to the most exacting standards. This specimen exhibits an impeccable exterior finish and an interior cabin that retains its original showroom integrity. Every mechanical system has been subjected to rigorous verification to ensure peak operational performance. For the discerning enthusiast who demands excellence, this offering represents a premier opportunity to acquire a motorcar in superlative condition.",
