    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is absolutely spotless\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and you won\u2019t find a single scratch or dent anywhere. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next big adventure. Come see it for yourself, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
