      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 in pristine condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54 straight-six engine paired with a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. Mechanically, this vehicle is sorted: the VANOS system has been professionally bulletproofed, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced. Performance is sharpened by a factory-spec limited-slip differential and a suspension refreshed with OEM bushings to maintain original turn-in characteristics. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, free of rock chips or oxidation. A truly turn-key example for the collector who values mechanical transparency and performance pedigree.",
